<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="about-content">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      At Tea, we leverage cutting-edge AI technology to personalize education, ensuring that every student receives tailored support aligned with their unique learning styles, interests, and academic levels. We strive to create an inclusive and nurturing environment for success.
    </p>
    
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>
      We design immersive learning experiences through dynamic content generation, interactive quizzes, and smart pop-up explanations, enhancing engagement and effectiveness. Our approach encourages deeper understanding, empowering students to take charge of their educational journeys.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to revolutionize education by delivering accessible and personalized learning experiences that empower students from all backgrounds to excel academically. We aim to foster growth, confidence, and a lifelong passion for learning.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Why Tea</h2>
    <p>
      We believe in the transformative potential of advanced AI to reshape the educational landscape, making learning interactive, intuitive, and enjoyable. Our goal is to empower every student to achieve their full potential.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 50px;
    background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Light background color for the About section */
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #333; /* Dark color for headings */
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #666; /* Slightly lighter color for body text */
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto; /* Center align paragraphs */
  }
</style>
